1031
01:11:12,174 --> 01:11:14,467
Možeš imati greške i
probleme, ali navuci ih...

1032
01:11:14,468 --> 01:11:16,009
na kraju...

1033
01:11:16,010 --> 01:11:18,554
i imat ćeš hit.

