01:12:45,702 --> 01:12:47,995
Bila je to luda vožnja.

1060
01:12:47,996 --> 01:12:52,228
Catrine kaže da želi
glumiti Casey. Molim te!

1061
01:12:52,332 --> 01:12:54,291
Molim te, Donalde.

1062
01:12:54,293 --> 01:12:56,501
CATRINE KINNER?

