1074
01:13:31,611 --> 01:13:33,737
HVALA. CHARLESE.

1075
01:13:33,738 --> 01:13:35,344
Zdravo.

1076
01:13:48,458 --> 01:13:50,980
Što bi ti učinio?

1077
01:13:51,293 --> 01:13:54,377
